General Notes about Licensing Conditions.

The ASKAP Software (ASKAPsoft) comprises of in-house ASKAP specific code
and open-source code.  All code written by staff and collaborators at
Australia Telescope National Facility (ATNF) is copyright
Commonwealth Scientific and Industrial Research Organisation (CSIRO).
This code is mostly found in the Code subdirectory and some of the
Tools/Dev subdirectory.
The open-source packages contained in the 3rdParty subdirectory
and some of the Tools subdirectory have their own licencing conditions.

The in-house code is released under the GPL version 2 licence.
